Getting Started

Prerequisites

· Python 3.8+
· NumPy, SciPy, Matplotlib
· Jupyter (for examples)

Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/M9-Framework.git
cd M9-Framework
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Quick Start

```python
from m9_core import M9Field, visualize_coherence

# Initialize a coherence field
field = M9Field(dimensions=9, resolution=0.1)

# Calculate stability gradient
stability = field.stability_gradient(parameters)

# Visualize
visualize_coherence(field)
```

